# Phase 1: Analyze the Fix

This is a patch for LoopVectorize:

[VPlan] Factor collectGroupedReplicateMemOps
Factor collectGroupedReplicateMemOps, enabling the reuse of canHoistOrSinkWithNoAliasCheck in hoistInvariantLoads.
